01:01:15.227 --> 01:01:21.467
Don't start confessing in your mind, what wrong you have done to yourself or anything - please, please, don't.

01:01:22.907 --> 01:01:30.407
And third condition is also very simple, if you understand, that you have to forgive everyone, in general.

01:01:32.927 --> 01:01:37.607
Now, this people sometimes say is very difficult but logically understand.

01:01:37.907 --> 01:01:43.047
Whether you forgive or don't forgive, you don't do anything - what do you do - nothing.

01:01:43.907 --> 01:01:47.047
But when you don't forgive, then you play into wrong hands.

01:01:47.367 --> 01:01:53.207
Those who wanted to trouble you, are happy while you are the one who is feeling extremely

01:01:53.447 --> 01:01:57.767
unhappy, all the time torturing yourself for the sake of others.

01:02:01.847 --> 01:02:07.567
So just forgive everyone - take it out of your mind. Now since I've come to Australia,

01:02:08.787 --> 01:02:15.107
I find, when I meet them, that they say, "Mother, difficult to forgive, difficult to forgive."

01:02:15.367 --> 01:02:20.367
I mean, there's nothing difficult - it's your own mental nonsense - throw it away.

01:02:20.927 --> 01:02:28.687
You'll feel so much lighter just now. Just say, "I forgive everyone." All those nonsensical people you need not even think of.

01:02:30.447 --> 01:02:35.427
In general, you should say, "I've forgiven everyone," and you'll be very much better off.

01:02:36.167 --> 01:02:40.367
These are the only three conditions, which are very easy - everybody can do it.

01:02:44.187 --> 01:02:51.187
Now, I have to request you, that you have to take out your shoes, if possible, because this Mother Earth really helps us a lot.

01:02:57.847 --> 01:03:03.087
Now those who are sitting on the ground, it's all right but those who are not sitting on the ground, have to know

01:03:03.627 --> 01:03:07.447
that you have to put your -

01:03:14.487 --> 01:03:18.967
you can come in front, if you like, can come in front -

01:03:20.767 --> 01:03:27.927
uh.. put your left foot away from the right because the left side represents

01:03:29.627 --> 01:03:37.187
our power of desire. Now, medical science doesn't make difference between the left lobe and the right lobe of the brain but we do.

01:03:39.947 --> 01:03:47.087
So we have to put the left foot away from the right foot and

01:03:50.307 --> 01:03:56.227
we have to use our left hand to express our pure desire to get Self-realization -

01:03:56.747 --> 01:03:59.707
is to put your left hand like this,

01:04:02.487 --> 01:04:08.307
just like this as he's showing, left hand and the right hand is

01:04:09.187 --> 01:04:13.427
the power of action. So, we'll use our right hand

01:04:13.747 --> 01:04:17.107
to give nourishment to our centers.

01:04:21.387 --> 01:04:27.787
This is to be done only today not all the time. Once you're realized, you don't have to do all this.

01:04:28.007 --> 01:04:35.427
This is just for your realization and also for you to know how you can raise your own Kundalini just now.

01:04:36.987 --> 01:04:44.247
So now, the left hand is towards Me suggesting that you are desirous of having Self-realization

01:04:45.947 --> 01:04:50.167
and the right hand is to be used for your action.

01:04:52.807 --> 01:05:00.807
I've already told you that I respect your freedom and those who do not want to have Self-realization

01:05:01.587 --> 01:05:05.267
should not watch others and sit here.

01:05:05.927 --> 01:05:11.507
They should go and that would be very civil of them, to do. But those who want

01:05:15.407 --> 01:05:20.947
can have it very easily. But

01:05:21.307 --> 01:05:27.387
whatever we get so easily without paying anything, sometimes we do not have respect for that.

01:05:28.547 --> 01:05:34.447
But you don't know, this is the most precious thing to become a Spirit

01:05:34.967 --> 01:05:42.287
and we should really respect the Self-realization and try to expand our awareness.

01:05:44.447 --> 01:05:49.167
So please, put left hand towards Me and now the right hand on your heart.

01:05:50.547 --> 01:05:53.667
In the heart resides the Spirit.

01:06:01.107 --> 01:06:07.487
If you become the Spirit, you become your own guide, your own master, your own guru.

01:06:08.767 --> 01:06:13.367
So, take your right hand in the upper portion of the abdomen

01:06:15.307 --> 01:06:22.967
which is the center of - on the left hand side. We're working only on the left hand side - which is the center of your mastery.

01:06:24.907 --> 01:06:31.387
Then you take your hand in the lower portion of the abdomen on the left hand side. This is the center

01:06:33.567 --> 01:06:41.027
of pure knowledge - knowledge of the Divine laws and how to work them out.

01:06:43.607 --> 01:06:47.447
When you get your Self-realization, you'll find,

01:06:47.667 --> 01:06:52.127
first time you'll feel this All-Pervading power on your finger-tips,

01:06:52.447 --> 01:06:57.687
Also you'll find a cool breeze coming out of your fontanel bone area,

01:06:58.407 --> 01:07:01.847
maybe warm in the beginning but later on cools down.

01:07:03.007 --> 01:07:09.907
So, this power that you get, you should know how to use it

01:07:10.447 --> 01:07:16.647
for your benevolence and for the benevolence of others. This is the pure knowledge.

01:07:17.227 --> 01:07:22.047
Now, please take your hand in the upper portion of your abdomen on the left hand side

01:07:25.147 --> 01:07:29.127
and now again on your heart.

01:07:36.827 --> 01:07:43.967
Now you have to put your right hand in the corner of your neck and your shoulder and turn your hand to your right.

01:07:46.287 --> 01:07:53.507
This center is caught up when you feel guilty and it's a very dangerous thing because

01:07:53.947 --> 01:08:01.447
when this, this center is out of gear, you get a horrible disease called Angina,

01:08:01.907 --> 01:08:09.727
you get spondylitis, also you get very lethargic organs. So please don't feel guilty.

01:08:10.607 --> 01:08:16.087
Now, raise your hand to your forehead across, put your thumb on one side

01:08:16.767 --> 01:08:21.567
and the fingers on the other and press it hard. Now, put it down your head.

01:08:22.507 --> 01:08:26.267
This is the center for forgiving others.

01:08:28.427 --> 01:08:35.467
Now, take this right hand - I'm just showing you now  and then we'll do it and I'll explain to you -

01:08:36.307 --> 01:08:43.767
on the back side of your head. Now, push back your head as far as possible. This is the center,

01:08:45.487 --> 01:08:51.387
without feeling guilty, without counting your mistakes, only for your satisfaction

01:08:51.627 --> 01:08:55.307
you have to ask forgiveness from this All-Pervading power.

01:08:56.827 --> 01:09:04.207
Now, stretch your hand fully - the palm is to stretch fully -

01:09:04.447 --> 01:09:11.747
and put the center of your palm on the fontanel bone area, which was a soft bone in your childhood.

01:09:12.307 --> 01:09:19.707
Now, put down your head as far as possible, now press it hard, your scalp, by pushing out

01:09:20.047 --> 01:09:28.687
your fingers outward. Now, this is very important - push them out and now press it and move your scalp seven times -

01:09:30.167 --> 01:09:35.907
you will know the reason for all this, why seven times you have to move it.

01:09:37.307 --> 01:09:43.047
Press your scalp and put down your head -

01:09:43.527 --> 01:09:49.127
clockwise, move it clockwise, seven times. That's all you have to do, that's all.

01:10:00.927 --> 01:10:07.447
Now, we have to close the eyes. You can take away your spectacles,

01:10:07.867 --> 01:10:11.507
please see that your both the feet are away from each other.

01:10:12.607 --> 01:10:19.807
If there's anything tight on your neck too much or on your waist, you can loosen it little bit and you have to be comfortable,

01:10:20.187 --> 01:10:27.067
not to slouch nor to stretch too much but in a comfortable state, way, you have to sit down.

01:10:29.447 --> 01:10:36.407
Now, please put the left hand towards Me, right hand on your heart and close your eyes.

01:10:36.867 --> 01:10:41.187
Here, you have to ask Me a question in your heart -

01:10:41.647 --> 01:10:47.447
you may call Me Mother or you may call Me Shri Mataji, whatever you feel like.

01:10:48.047 --> 01:10:54.827
Ask a question in your heart, three times - a very fundamental question about yourself

01:10:55.067 --> 01:10:58.307
"Mother, am I the Spirit?"

01:10:58.527 --> 01:11:04.347
"Mother, am I the Spirit?" ask this question three times in your heart.

01:11:26.927 --> 01:11:33.527
If you are the Spirit, you are your master. So please, put your right hand

01:11:33.767 --> 01:11:39.827
on the upper portion of your abdomen on the left hand side and press it with your fingers - not very hard.

01:11:40.367 --> 01:11:48.367
Here you ask another fundamental question in your heart, three times, "Mother, am I my own master?"

01:11:49.787 --> 01:11:52.947
With full confidence ask this question.

01:12:02.227 --> 01:12:07.927
Again, I cannot cross over your freedom - I respect it

01:12:08.307 --> 01:12:13.667
and I cannot force pure knowledge on you - you have to ask for it.

01:12:14.127 --> 01:12:21.327
So, please take your right hand in the lower portion of your abdomen and press it hard.

01:12:22.287 --> 01:12:25.627
on the left hand side. Here

01:12:27.407 --> 01:12:32.187
please say six times because this center has got six petals.

01:12:34.267 --> 01:12:42.167
"Mother, please give me pure knowledge. Mother, please give me pure knowledge," ask this six times.

01:12:52.187 --> 01:12:58.567
As soon as you ask for pure knowledge, the Kundalini starts moving upward.

01:13:01.167 --> 01:13:04.127
So now,

01:13:05.247 --> 01:13:10.407
with full confidence you have to open your higher centers.

01:13:11.887 --> 01:13:16.667
Please, raise your right hand on the left hand side

01:13:17.127 --> 01:13:21.087
of your abdomen in the upper portion and press it hard.

01:13:23.487 --> 01:13:29.747
Here, you have to say with full confidence, ten times,

01:13:30.947 --> 01:13:36.267
"Mother, I am my own master." Say it with full confidence,

01:13:37.307 --> 01:13:45.107
complete self-confidence. "Mother, I am my own master." You have to say it ten times.

01:13:50.867 --> 01:13:56.847
We have to know that we are not this body, this mind,

01:13:57.347 --> 01:14:03.847
this intellect, emotions, conditionings, ego

01:14:04.507 --> 01:14:08.267
but we are pure Spirit.

01:14:10.387 --> 01:14:16.887
This is the fundamental truth about yourself. So now, please raise your right hand

01:14:17.647 --> 01:14:23.447
on your heart and with full confidence say, twelve times,

01:14:23.947 --> 01:14:29.507
please say it twelve times, "Mother, I am the pure Spirit."

01:14:29.947 --> 01:14:34.447
Please say it twelve times, "Mother, I am the,

01:14:34.707 --> 01:14:38.867
I am the pure Spirit," twelve times, please.

01:14:49.947 --> 01:14:57.127
Another thing we have to know that this All-Pervading power of God's love,

01:14:57.667 --> 01:15:03.687
is the ocean of knowledge, is the ocean of compassion and bliss

01:15:04.027 --> 01:15:11.347
but above all, it is the ocean of forgiveness and whatever mistakes we might have committed

01:15:11.647 --> 01:15:17.627
can be easily dissolved by the power of this ocean of forgiveness.

01:15:18.167 --> 01:15:24.747
So, please forgive yourself and now raise your right hand in the corner of your neck and your shoulder,

01:15:26.067 --> 01:15:30.587
push it as far back as possible and turn your head to your right.

01:15:32.527 --> 01:15:35.667
Here, you have to say sixteen times,

01:15:38.627 --> 01:15:44.867
with full confidence, "Mother, I am not guilty at all."

01:15:47.567 --> 01:15:50.567
Please say it sixteen times.

01:15:52.267 --> 01:15:56.847
You don't judge yourself, let your Kundalini judge.

01:15:58.127 --> 01:16:05.087
"Mother, I am not guilty at all," please say it sixteen times.

01:16:05.407 --> 01:16:10.287
This center has the maximum number of petals - sixteen petals.

01:16:10.607 --> 01:16:17.287
This center looks after your ear, nose, throat, face, everything, your tongue, your eyes.

01:16:27.387 --> 01:16:31.887
I have already told you whether you forgive or don't forgive, you don't do anything

01:16:32.187 --> 01:16:36.347
but if you don't forgive then you play into wrong hands

01:16:38.507 --> 01:16:45.967
so, in general, you have to forgive everyone not remembering anyone of the people who have troubled you.

01:16:46.787 --> 01:16:49.967
Now, raise your right hand

01:16:50.687 --> 01:16:55.867
on your forehead, across, put your thumb on one side

01:16:57.807 --> 01:17:02.347
and fingers on the other. Now press it hard.

01:17:03.247 --> 01:17:06.587
Please bend your head as far as possible.

01:17:08.967 --> 01:17:13.707
Here, without thinking of anybody else

01:17:14.547 --> 01:17:20.727
just, in general, you have to say, "Mother, I forgive everyone."

01:17:22.487 --> 01:17:30.047
or, "Mother, I forgive everyone in general." Say it from your heart, not how many times but from your heart.

01:17:44.007 --> 01:17:50.187
Now, please take your hand on the back side of your head and push it back as far as possible.

01:17:52.067 --> 01:17:59.647
Here, without feeling guilty, without counting your mistakes, you have to say

01:18:02.387 --> 01:18:08.347
with full confidence, "Oh Divine power, please forgive me

01:18:09.067 --> 01:18:14.747
if I have done anything wrong against you knowingly or unknowingly.

01:18:15.647 --> 01:18:22.187
"Oh Divine power, please forgive me if I have done anything wrong against you

01:18:22.347 --> 01:18:30.147
knowingly or unknowingly." This you're going to say for your satisfaction from your heart - not how many times.

01:18:40.227 --> 01:18:45.347
Now the last center which is very important. Please stretch your hand

01:18:51.027 --> 01:18:58.467
and put the center of your palm on top of the fontanel bone area which was the soft bone in your childhood.

01:19:03.527 --> 01:19:09.087
Please put down your head as far as possible, push back your fingers.

01:19:17.427 --> 01:19:25.387
Please push back your fingers, put a good pressure on your scalp. Here again, I respect your freedom -

01:19:26.407 --> 01:19:32.507
I cannot force Self-realization on you so you have to say seven times,

01:19:32.867 --> 01:19:38.827
"Mother, please give me Self-realization, my second birth,"

01:19:40.007 --> 01:19:46.187
and you just move your scalp, very slowly, seven times,  saying that.

01:19:51.507 --> 01:19:55.727
[SHRI MATAJI BLOWS INTO THE MICROPHONE]

01:19:56.507 --> 01:20:00.767
