01:20:02.087 --> 01:20:07.887
[SHRI MATAJI BLOWS INTO THE MICROPHONE] Push back your fingers, push back, push back your fingers other there's no pressure.

01:20:08.107 --> 01:20:14.967
Put down your heads, please put down, put down your heads. Please put down your heads, push back your finger.

01:20:15.267 --> 01:20:18.367
[SHRI MATAJI BLOWS INTO THE MICROPHONE]

01:20:18.807 --> 01:20:22.807
[SHRI MATAJI BLOWS INTO THE MICROPHONE]

01:20:23.307 --> 01:20:27.367
[SHRI MATAJI BLOWS INTO THE MICROPHONE]

01:20:27.607 --> 01:20:31.307
[SHRI MATAJI BLOWS INTO THE MICROPHONE]

01:20:31.607 --> 01:20:36.827
[SHRI MATAJI BLOWS INTO THE MICROPHONE]

01:20:37.307 --> 01:20:43.987
Now, please take down your hands. Put both the hands towards Me, like this.

01:20:45.307 --> 01:20:51.387
Open your eyes, you can wear your spectacles also. Put both the hands towards Me, like this.

01:20:52.307 --> 01:21:00.027
Now, put the right hand towards Me, like this, put down your head and see for yourself if there's a cool or a hot

01:21:00.747 --> 01:21:03.687
breeze like waves coming from your head.

01:21:04.787 --> 01:21:10.547
Bend your head and see for yourself. Don't put your hand on top of your head, away from it.

01:21:10.787 --> 01:21:17.507
Some people get it far away, some get it nearer. Just see, if there's a cool or a hot breeze coming inside.

01:21:26.527 --> 01:21:30.027
Now, please put the left hand towards Me

01:21:33.087 --> 01:21:39.107
and bend your head and see for yourself now

01:21:40.007 --> 01:21:45.367
with the right hand, if there's a cool or a hot breeze coming out of your head.

01:21:53.267 --> 01:21:57.827
Again with the right hand, please try again with the right hand.

01:22:07.147 --> 01:22:11.287
See yourself, if there's a cool or a hot breeze coming.

01:22:15.147 --> 01:22:20.127
Now, raise your both the hands towards the sky, like this

01:22:23.887 --> 01:22:31.727
and ask a question, three times, "Mother, is this the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost?"

01:22:34.247 --> 01:22:39.707
Or you can ask, "Mother, is this the All-Pervading power of God's love?"

01:22:40.767 --> 01:22:48.167
Or you can ask, "Mother, is this the Param Chaitanya?" Ask anyone of these questions. These are the names of only one

01:22:48.587 --> 01:22:56.407
thing which is the All-Pervading power of Divine love which does all the living work.

01:22:56.947 --> 01:23:00.147
Just ask anyone of these questions, three times

01:23:02.947 --> 01:23:10.907
Push back your head towards the sky. Please, put down your hands now.

01:23:13.127 --> 01:23:16.227
Just put the hands like this.

01:23:20.147 --> 01:23:26.447
You can become thoughtless, you can watch Me without thinking. Just put [UNCLEAR]

01:23:27.667 --> 01:23:33.087
Now, those who have felt - please put down your hands

01:23:34.547 --> 01:23:37.987
Put your hands like this. Now,

01:23:39.967 --> 01:23:47.327
those who have felt cool or warm or hot breeze like waves

01:23:47.567 --> 01:23:51.747
on the fingers, on the hands

01:23:51.987 --> 01:23:57.247
or out of the fontanel bone area please raise both your hands.

01:24:03.467 --> 01:24:08.347
So, that's it! May God bless you!

01:24:08.607 --> 01:24:13.047
Everyone seems to have got it except for very few people who haven't.

01:24:14.287 --> 01:24:20.487
Very few didn't get it - doesn't matter, you'll get it tomorrow, it's all right.

01:24:21.107 --> 01:24:27.427
You shouldn't doubt, that's the main point is the doubting and you should forgive, most of you.

01:24:28.267 --> 01:24:33.647
Except for 3-4 people, I think, most of you have got it so, May god bless you!.

01:24:35.367 --> 01:24:40.227
I hope to see you tomorrow again and tomorrow

01:24:40.467 --> 01:24:44.527
I'll meet all of you, individually, all of you.

01:24:45.007 --> 01:24:52.027
Now, you have to inform your friends and everyone, that they should come and we should have more people

01:24:54.007 --> 01:24:59.487
because I'm here only for tomorrow and then I'll come back after two years,

01:24:59.687 --> 01:25:06.187
one year. I shouldn't say two years, will  be too much. All right, so I would request you

01:25:06.427 --> 01:25:12.867
that you should inform your friends, you should inform your relations

01:25:13.207 --> 01:25:16.507
because this is the only thing you can give it to them.

01:25:17.767 --> 01:25:21.347
Now, you have reached a state where you are thoughtless,

01:25:21.647 --> 01:25:28.707
so don't argue with people who haven't got it. Those who haven't got it will also get it tomorrow and those who have got it,

01:25:29.427 --> 01:25:34.027
should know that you have to maintain it - like keeping the peace in your heart

01:25:34.427 --> 01:25:37.827
and not arguing about it and quarreling with others

01:25:38.067 --> 01:25:43.207
because those who won't get it will start saying something - doesn't matter, makes no difference.

01:25:43.527 --> 01:25:49.507
You have got it, so keep your experience with yourself and we have to share it with others, so many

01:25:49.767 --> 01:25:52.747
in Melbourne. May God bless you!

